story.title: Beta - Episode 5
story.storyDescription: Everyone's dying to download Rezurekt, the hottest new app — even its creators.
story.creator: web-uploader

author.bio: EJ Hendricks is a writer with a passion for new media. She resides in New York City with her cat.

story.prePaywallNotification: Why is Jake’s body in a tank?! Is Emma in danger? Keep reading BETA to find out!
story.postPaywallNotification: What does Tim’s confession mean? Will Emma make it out alive? Tap back into Hooked to keep reading!

messages.text: Emma looks at Tim with worry in her eyes…
Suddenly, alarms start to blare.
What’s going on??
We have to go. Now.
The lights shut off.
Alarms blare.
Emma and Tim run.
They are separated in the confusion.
Minutes later…
Tim?? I can’t find you.
These alarms are SO loud.
And there are guards everywhere…
I’m just trying to find a place to hide.
Update: I’m in a supply closet. Please let me know that you’re okay.
I’m scared, Tim.
I think it was his body, Tim. I really think it was.
But why?? What were all those cables for, those wires?
These alarms keep getting louder. Even in this closet I can barely think.
Where are you?
Where are YOU?!
Trying to find you.
Can you drop a pin? There’s so many doors.
Are you just walking around out there? There are guards everywhere!
Tim, how did they even know we were here??
SHIT, TIM!!! Were those gunshots?
Those were definitely gunshots.
Tim?? You’re scaring me. Please respond.
I’m panicking. What if they shot you?
I need to get out of this closet before they find me but I feel paralyzed. I’m so scared.
If you’re dead I’ll never forgive myself.
I dragged you here. I made you take me down there. I made you help me.
It’s bad enough that Jake died for…this. This app. And now you, too?
I’m not dead, Emma.
Are you safe?
Look, don’t worry about me. Seriously, don’t.
What the hell is going on?
When Q hired me…
He hired me for you.
To keep an eye on you.
To monitor your conversations with Jake.
To see how the beta was working. To see what Jake would say.
You were hired to SPY on me??!
What the hell, Tim?!
So you knew.
The entire time you knew. You knew you were helping…a murderer?
No!
I don’t know what that’s about. I swear.
It was just to keep an eye on things. That’s all he asked.
And everything else?
Our date, or whatever that was — was fake?
It was supposed to be.
But once I got to know you…it became real.
Stop.
It’s true. I do have feelings for you, Emma. Real feelings.
And I’m sure you hate me right now.
Yup.
But I’m done with the lies. I’m done with Q. All that matters is that I get you out of here safe.
So please, just listen to me.
I’m going to distract the guards. Just hide for a few more minutes and I’ll give you a signal.
And then you run.
And then what, Tim? Q will be waiting outside to capture me, and kill me too?
Use me in some sort of…sick experiment?
No.
I swear, I’m going to get you out of here alive. No matter what.
INCOMING MESSAGE FROM REZUREKT -- ___USER:__JAKE___SCHIPP
Jake, now’s not a good time.
I did a quick search of the payroll — Q has been paying Tim out of his own account.
Please don’t say I told you so.
I’m not going to.
If this guy’s coming clean, chances are he’s telling the truth about getting you out of there.
And right now that’s all that matters.
So now you want me to trust Tim. After everything he just said?
If it means you get out of there alive…yes.
I don’t know what to do.
I keep hearing footsteps. Boots. Shouting. They’re everywhere.
Jake, why is Q doing this?
Why did he kill you? Why does he…have your body?
I have some ideas, but we can’t talk about that now.
I’m sending you a pin. It’s a service exit, they won’t expect you there.
I’m going to be sending it to Tim, too. So he can draw the guards’ attention away from there.
When he gives you the signal, you run for that door, and you don’t look back. Got it?
Wait, now you’re talking to Tim?!
Anything I’ve gotta do to get you out.
Wait—
Everything just got quiet.
The alarms stopped—
Manual override. It wasn’t easy, but—
That was you?!
Tim’s drawing them away.
You need to go—
Jake, I don’t understand—
RUN, NOW!
Emma runs from the building. She doesn’t look back. She doesn’t stop until she reaches her car.
She drives for miles, and pulls into a dark, empty parking lot.
She calls 911 and reports a crime at Rezurekt HQ.
But, before she does…
Jake, I think things are about to get bad.
Are you safe now??!
I can’t find you on the map. Did you turn off location services?
Whatever happens…
I love you Jake. I always have. From the moment I met you. And I always will.
Emma, what’s going on-
Emma closes Rezurekt…
And throws her phone to the ground, SMASHING it to pieces.
